last_episode_to_air.name: Lagos with WizKid, Ice Prince
last_episode_to_air.overview: We chase Wizkid on his ascent into the musical stratosphere.

name: Noisey
overview: A first-hand look into the cultures and artists behind some of the world’s most compelling music scenes.

episodes.name: Bompton with Kendrick Lamar
episodes.overview: Zach travels to Compton to meet Kendrick Lamar and the friends he grew up with, many of whom are members of the notorious Piru gang.

episodes.name: São Paulo with Major Lazer, MC Guime
episodes.overview: Zach heads to São Paulo to meet Major Lazer and explore the violence surrounding baile funk.

episodes.name: Miami with Rick Ross, DJ Khaled
episodes.overview: Zach heads to Miami to meet Rick Ross, DJ Khaled, and talk about how immigration and drug trafficking have shaped the city.

episodes.name: Chicago with Chief Keef, Vic Mensa
episodes.overview: Zach heads to Chicago's South Side to meet Chief Keef, Common, and talk about how drill music grew out of violence and segregation in the city.

episodes.name: Jamaica with Popcaan, Chronixx
episodes.overview: Zach goes to Jamaica to meet Popcaan, Chronixx and talk about Vybz Kartel.

episodes.name: Las Vegas with Tiësto, Justin Bieber
episodes.overview: Zach heads to Vegas to meet Justin Bieber and Wayne Newton, as well as DJs Steve Angello and Tiesto, to find out what life is like for the world's highest paid DJs.

episodes.name: Detroit with Big Sean, Danny Brown
episodes.overview: Zach heads to Detroit to meet Big Sean and Danny Brown, and see how the city is rebounding from the brink of collapse.

episodes.name: London with Giggs, Skepta, Jammer
episodes.overview: Zach heads to London to meet the rising stars of British hip-hop and grime, like Jammer, Giggs, JME, and Skepta.

episodes.name: Chicago: The City Speaks
episodes.overview: NOISEY returns to Chicago for an emotional town hall meeting to screen their episode for residents and community leaders

episodes.name: YG and the Therapist
episodes.overview: Shot three times by unidentified gunmen, YG turned to alcohol to cope with his paranoia. On the eve of his new record dropping, NOISEY filmed YG's first attempt at therapy.

episodes.name: Bay Area with G-Easy and E-40
episodes.overview: Police brutality and gentrification mean Black Lives Matter plays a big role in Bay Area rap culture. G-Eazy, E-40, Nef the Pharoah and more explore these topics.

episodes.name: Nashville With Kesha, Jelly Roll
episodes.overview: Hustlers, rebels and outsiders in the country music capital of the world.

episodes.name: Paris with Niska, MHD, Medine
episodes.overview: The second biggest hip-hop market on earth has been in a state of emergency since 2015, following the deadliest terrorist attacks on French soil in 100 years.

episodes.name: Seoul with Big Bang
episodes.overview: Inside the K-Pop training academies where teenagers give their all to be the next big thing; starring the Justin Bieber of K-Pop, Taeyang from Big Bang.

episodes.name: Atlanta with Young Thug, Migos
episodes.overview: In the hip-hop capital of the world, Young Thug, Killer Mike, Migos, 21 Savage, Lil Yachty and more explore the evolution of trap music, from drug houses to the Top 40.

episodes.name: Lagos with WizKid, Ice Prince
episodes.overview: We chase Wizkid on his ascent into the musical stratosphere.
